{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/prototype/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"나의-이해를-위해서\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C\" aria-label=\"나의 이해를 위해서 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>나의 이해를 위해서</h1>\n<p>이 글은 본인의 이해를 위해 작성된 글이므로 단어나 설명이 이상할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>지적은 언제나 환영입니다. :)</p>\n<h1 id=\"프로토타입-천천히-보자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%86%A0%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-%EC%B2%9C%EC%B2%9C%ED%9E%88-%EB%B3%B4%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"프로토타입 천천히 보자 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로토타입, 천천히 보자</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1번</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> korName <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 5번</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> usName <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">setName</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Kim\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>korName<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>setName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// f(){ return 'Kim' }</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>usName<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>setName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// f(){ return 'Kim' }</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>함수를 선언하면 생성자함수가 생기며, 생성된 함수에안에 prototype프로퍼티가 존재하고, 그와 별개로 프로토타입객체가 생긴다.</li>\n</ol>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/5f37644b549e499b72142a86f864ef49/bca35/prototype01.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 39.189189189189186%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"prototype01\" title=\"prototype01\" src=\"/static/5f37644b549e499b72142a86f864ef49/fcda8/prototype01.png\" srcset=\"/static/5f37644b549e499b72142a86f864ef49/12f09/prototype01.png 148w,\n/static/5f37644b549e499b72142a86f864ef49/e4a3f/prototype01.png 295w,\n/static/5f37644b549e499b72142a86f864ef49/fcda8/prototype01.png 590w,\n/static/5f37644b549e499b72142a86f864ef49/bca35/prototype01.png 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>프로토타입객체 안에는 constructor속성이 있으며 프로토타입객체가 어떤 객체에서 상속되었는지 가르키고있다.\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/8bd09c6ca529cca86c2fc100fb06117b/394f7/prototype03.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 84.45945945945947%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"prototype03\" title=\"prototype03\" src=\"/static/8bd09c6ca529cca86c2fc100fb06117b/fcda8/prototype03.png\" srcset=\"/static/8bd09c6ca529cca86c2fc100fb06117b/12f09/prototype03.png 148w,\n/static/8bd09c6ca529cca86c2fc100fb06117b/e4a3f/prototype03.png 295w,\n/static/8bd09c6ca529cca86c2fc100fb06117b/fcda8/prototype03.png 590w,\n/static/8bd09c6ca529cca86c2fc100fb06117b/394f7/prototype03.png 707w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>prototype 프로퍼티는 선언된 함수에 있다.</li>\n<li>prototype 프로퍼티는 그 함수의 프로토타입객체를 가르킨다.\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 511px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/64aa7402721b3c3b396262172a5bb69d/92e00/prototype02.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 85.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"prototype02\" title=\"prototype02\" src=\"/static/64aa7402721b3c3b396262172a5bb69d/92e00/prototype02.png\" srcset=\"/static/64aa7402721b3c3b396262172a5bb69d/12f09/prototype02.png 148w,\n/static/64aa7402721b3c3b396262172a5bb69d/e4a3f/prototype02.png 295w,\n/static/64aa7402721b3c3b396262172a5bb69d/92e00/prototype02.png 511w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 511px) 100vw, 511px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ol>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/63883d13dd1c6b9d2f88fe4c1d378459/442cb/prototype04.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 36.486486486486484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"prototype04\" title=\"prototype04\" src=\"/static/63883d13dd1c6b9d2f88fe4c1d378459/fcda8/prototype04.png\" srcset=\"/static/63883d13dd1c6b9d2f88fe4c1d378459/12f09/prototype04.png 148w,\n/static/63883d13dd1c6b9d2f88fe4c1d378459/e4a3f/prototype04.png 295w,\n/static/63883d13dd1c6b9d2f88fe4c1d378459/fcda8/prototype04.png 590w,\n/static/63883d13dd1c6b9d2f88fe4c1d378459/442cb/prototype04.png 752w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>이때 새로운 인스턴스를 생성하면 그 인스턴스에  __proto__ 속성이 생긴다.</li>\n</ol>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 314px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/32483ddffba6a31624911ef4af47dfa9/5b158/prototype05.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"prototype05\" title=\"prototype05\" src=\"/static/32483ddffba6a31624911ef4af47dfa9/5b158/prototype05.png\" srcset=\"/static/32483ddffba6a31624911ef4af47dfa9/12f09/prototype05.png 148w,\n/static/32483ddffba6a31624911ef4af47dfa9/e4a3f/prototype05.png 295w,\n/static/32483ddffba6a31624911ef4af47dfa9/5b158/prototype05.png 314w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 314px) 100vw, 314px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>__proto__ 속성은 생성자 함수를 가르키지 않고 프로토타입객체를 가르킨다. 4번처럼.\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/2381f70cc6b69c2933efd9539b9d9e44/f4b77/prototype06.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 59.45945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"prototype06\" title=\"prototype06\" src=\"/static/2381f70cc6b69c2933efd9539b9d9e44/fcda8/prototype06.png\" srcset=\"/static/2381f70cc6b69c2933efd9539b9d9e44/12f09/prototype06.png 148w,\n/static/2381f70cc6b69c2933efd9539b9d9e44/e4a3f/prototype06.png 295w,\n/static/2381f70cc6b69c2933efd9539b9d9e44/fcda8/prototype06.png 590w,\n/static/2381f70cc6b69c2933efd9539b9d9e44/f4b77/prototype06.png 770w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>그래서 인스턴스는 생성자 함수와 똑같이 프로토타입객체를 바라 보게된다. (같은 address를 참조하게 된다.)\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 256px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/17a8d9625a0480e31fd74dec2989a46e/6f3f2/prototype07.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"prototype07\" title=\"prototype07\" src=\"/static/17a8d9625a0480e31fd74dec2989a46e/6f3f2/prototype07.png\" srcset=\"/static/17a8d9625a0480e31fd74dec2989a46e/12f09/prototype07.png 148w,\n/static/17a8d9625a0480e31fd74dec2989a46e/6f3f2/prototype07.png 256w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>\n<p>그러므로 프로토타입객체의 속성을 변경하면 변경사항이 인스턴스의 속성에도 적용된다. (참조에 의한 호출로 동작한다.)\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/ac43f432db303cf90afcb6c2f72640b8/cab43/prototype08.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 83.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"prototype08\" title=\"prototype08\" src=\"/static/ac43f432db303cf90afcb6c2f72640b8/fcda8/prototype08.png\" srcset=\"/static/ac43f432db303cf90afcb6c2f72640b8/12f09/prototype08.png 148w,\n/static/ac43f432db303cf90afcb6c2f72640b8/e4a3f/prototype08.png 295w,\n/static/ac43f432db303cf90afcb6c2f72640b8/fcda8/prototype08.png 590w,\n/static/ac43f432db303cf90afcb6c2f72640b8/cab43/prototype08.png 755w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">setName</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Kim\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>console.log (korName.setName); // f(){ return 'Kim' }\nconsole.log (usName.setName); // f(){ return 'Kim' }</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># 참고\n- [프로토타입 이해하기](https://medium.com/@bluesh55/javascript-prototype-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-f8e67c286b67)\n\n- [기발자의 한 놈만 패는 JavaScript 7교시 - 프로토타입 편](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zbgKZVMzdfk)</code></pre></div>","excerpt":"나의 이해를 위해서 이 글은 본인의 이해를 위해 작성된 글이므로 단어나 설명이 이상할 수 있습니다. 지적은 언제나 환영입니다. :) 프로토타입, 천천히 보자 함수를 선언하면 생성자함수가 생기며, 생성된 함수에안에 prototype프로퍼티가 존재하고,…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/prototype/#%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C\">나의 이해를 위해서</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/prototype/#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%86%A0%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-%EC%B2%9C%EC%B2%9C%ED%9E%88-%EB%B3%B4%EC%9E%90\">프로토타입, 천천히 보자</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/prototype/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"자바스크립트 protortype 이해하기","date":"Feb 01, 2018","tags":["javascript"],"keywords":["R0k's l0g","padawanR0k"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/prototype/","series":[],"lastmod":"2018-02-01"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}